275
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:39,760
Roan!

276
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:41,320
Ne!

277
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,810
Maaya!

278
00:18:51,810 --> 00:18:53,330
Maaya...

279
00:19:09,090 --> 00:19:10,620
Maaya?

280
00:19:10,620 --> 00:19:11,950
Maaya!

281
00:19:17,330 --> 00:19:21,000
Yuufa... Takius...

282
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,630
Maaya...

283
00:19:28,070 --> 00:19:29,740
Huh?

284
00:19:29,740 --> 00:19:31,850
Roan...

285
00:19:31,850 --> 00:19:34,410
Huh?! Yuufa!

286
00:19:34,410 --> 00:19:36,520
Roan, jsi v pořádku?

287
00:19:36,520 --> 00:19:38,790
Jo, ale nemůžu se hýbat. 

288
00:19:38,790 --> 00:19:39,790
A co ty? 

289
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:43,320
Jsem v pořádku, ale Takius ... 

290
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:43,980
Huh?

291
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:48,660
Takius!

292
00:19:48,660 --> 00:19:51,650
